i need to rant, read if you want, i kinda tapped into my deeper thoughts and philosophy.i have a whole part about emma and charlotte and the rest. read if you want.

i dont think i ever saw the world the same way i'm seeing it right now. its winter. its fucking winter. and i fucking love it. i dont think any season could ever make me feel the same way as winter does. that perfect crisp cool, perfected weather. the way your warm breath feels as you breath in and out, on your cold chapped lips. i dunno something about all the feelings i associate with winter gets me all giggly and happy. winter makes me happy, its a happy season. Yesterday i did alot of thinking more thinking than i've done in awhile. i never typed it all out because i was sick, and not in the mood to even breathe. But i realized i'm in a point in my life where every move i take counts. like i'm being watched, but in a judgemental way. i feel as if the only thing in the world keeping me together is my art and my friends. I'll start with Emma. Emma, i love you, you defiantly inspire me to do amazing things. you are one of the greatest people in the world, your an amazing artist, and i can only prey that i can study the arts enough to become as amazing as you. you introduced me to so many great bands (the motherfucking used, glassjaw, and i THINK it was you who told me about elliott smith). Now Sarah. Sarah, you are an amazing personin so many diffrent ways. i've only read some of your poetry, but you could become something amazing if thats what you wanted, but you of course are already somthing amazing and beautiful. the way you can put words together and make them flow into eachother as if the words were made to go with each other. Charlotte, you should know by now how much i love you, i wrote a fucking essay about you how much more could you ask for? we've shared so much together in the short times we see each other. and we've had extrodianary experiences. Zoe, you are such a beautiful and sponatious thinker, i am truly graced to know someone like you. I am graced  know someone like all of you. Eva, your so silly and great to be around. you make every situation a  happy one, regardless of the circumstances. all of you are so extrodinaryly special to me, and so is the city. i somtimes think i'm going to collapse and give in if i dont see you guys. i love you guys so much, and i swear to fucking god if i had to i'd kill myself over killing any of you.one day i'll go to ellington, i'll furfill my dream of being in DC with you guys studying the one thing i pour my heart into. I need to find a way to move there, i might just have to run away and escape if thats what it takes. but emma, you and me and our plan needs to work, if we dont work our plan, i have no idea what else we'd do. start thinking, i'll keep dreaming. GOD SAVES.

love, 

.::. Haley .::.
